    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people say things get better, but they dont get it. i've spent years in therapy, years trying to 'rebuild,' and i just keep hitting the same walls. it's like trying to fix a machine that was built with faulty parts from the start. at some point, isnt it just more logical to accept that some things just aren't meant to be fixed?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
